title: BRIEF-Hawaiian Electric Industries Says American Savings Bank Q4 Net Income $16.9 Mln vs $16.2 Mln Last Year

Jan 30 (Reuters) - Hawaiian Electric Industries Inc:
* AMERICAN SAVINGS BANK REPORTS 2017 YEAR-END AND FOURTH QUARTER EARNINGS
* AMERICAN SAVINGS BANK‘S Q4 2017 NET INTEREST INCOME WAS $57.0 MILLION, COMPARED TO $53.0 MILLION IN Q4 OF 2016
* SAYS ‍AMERICAN SAVINGS BANK‘S NET INCOME FOR Q4 WAS $16.9 MILLION VERSUS $16.2 MILLION IN Q4 OF 2016​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
